  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "$ 20 million from the US",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "US President Joe Biden announced today (28) at the G7 Summit that US $ 20 million will be provided as additional assistance to Sri Lanka.",
        "It is said that the money will be used to strengthen food security in Sri Lanka. The US Embassy said the financial assistance will be used to feed 800,000 school children under the School Nutrition Program, provide food vouchers to 27,000 pregnant mothers over the next 15 months, and provide agricultural and financial assistance to 30,000 farmers to increase food production in Sri Lanka. Announced."
      ],
